            "id": 6408721,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 永光(1711)股價殺至跌停，跌停價33.75元，成交24,032張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>永光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1711-TW</a>)07日10:14下跌3.75元，股價跌停報33.75元，委買1,383張、委賣88張，成交24,032張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為色料化學品,特用化學品,電子化學品,碳粉產品,醫藥化學品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>永光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1711-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.57%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.17%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-473 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-131 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-342 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,160 張</li> <li>融券增減：+46 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
